# SUPER_SALES_DASHBOARD

## Project Overview

This project is an interactive Super Store Sales Dashboard created using Power BI.  
The dashboard helps analyze sales performance, profit trends, customer segments, shipping modes, and product categories using visual analytics.

The main objective of this project is to convert raw sales data into meaningful business insights through interactive dashboards and visualizations.


## Dashboard Features

- Sales Analysis by Month and Year
- Profit Analysis by Month and Year
- Sales by Category and Sub-Category
- Sales by Ship Mode
- Sales by Customer Segment
- Sales by Payment Mode
- Region Filter (Central, East, South, West)

### KPI Cards Included
- Total Sales
- Total Quantity
- Total Profit
- Average Rating


## Tools and Technologies Used

- Power BI
- Excel / CSV Dataset
- Data Cleaning
- Data Transformation
- DAX Functions
- Data Visualization


## Dataset Information

The dataset contains information related to:

- Orders
- Customers
- Sales
- Profit
- Shipping
- Product Categories
- Payment Modes
- Regions


